{
  "stem": "9701.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] My mother got a pair of scissors and cut open the sleeves on his jacket and sort of peeled him out of the jacket.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They then went to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I did not see his body.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I don't know how bad it looked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But later that day my father had what was probably a mild heart attack.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And remember I said earlier that Jewish doctors weren't allowed to practice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there wasn't a Jewish doctor in the village anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And Christian doctors weren't allowed to practice-- I mean, weren't allowed to treat Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But my mother got word to our doctor, who was Christian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this man took tremendous risk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "By the way, his name was Dr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Bruno, B-R-U-N-O, Weber, W-E-B-E-R.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He came late at night to our home and he treated my father until he was well again.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Now, we lived in the village.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And everyone knew who everybody is and where everybody lived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So this man literally risked his life because had he been seen, who knows what would've happened to him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He would have been sent to a concentration camp, lost his life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Who knows what would've happened to his family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I just want to give a little aside about this doctor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "In 1990 when I was back in the village, I was looking for him because I wanted to thank him and learned that he's no longer alive.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But I found his sister.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I talked to her and thanked her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Someone listened to that conversation and took me aside later on and said, you don't know the whole story about this doctor, do you?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said no, what is the rest of the story?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
